# OSLogPreferences

**Property List Key**

A dictionary that defines the logging configuration profile for the app.

## Discussion

The keys and values you use in this dictionary are the same as those you use in a logging configuration profile property list file, described in [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/os/customizing-logging-behavior-while-debugging].
